headline: AHEAD Appoints Sumed Marwaha as Managing Director, India
summary: AHEAD, a leading provider of enterprise cloud solutions and digital platform engineering, has appointed Sumed Marwaha as Managing Director, India. In this role, he will lead AHEAD's rapidly expanding operations in India and further strengthen its position as a global center of excellence for delivery, innovation and client success.

headline: KeenStack Launches AI-Powered Healthcare Referral Management Solution Powered by the ServiceNow AI Platform
summary: KeenStack, the professional services consulting firm that helps companies unlock the full potential of ServiceNow, today announces the launch of its AI-powered Healthcare Referral Management Solution. Built on ServiceNow, the system streamlines referral intake, validation, and routing—reducing delays, improving handoffs, and accelerating patient access.
